data.description:
Pictures from a previous listing.

Horses? Want a pool? Come, make your horses happy at YOUR VERY OWN 2.5 ACRE ENGLISH COUNTRYSIDE ESTATE complete with a 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath 3345 SF Tudor home w/upstairs bonus room that could be a 5 bedroom, an over-sized IN-GROUND POOL & 4-stall horse barn, shower area & tack room w/ample fenced/cross-fenced room for your horses to roam! Walk onto your covered front porch, open the double front doors & enter into the Grand Entry Foyer w/tile floors, a Formal Living Room off to one side & a staircase leading to the upstairs bedrooms. Chef's dream kitchen includes an island w/cook top, tons of cabinets, oodles of stone counter-top space, stainless appliances, including a top-of-the-line side-by-side fridge & a breakfast nook that overlooks the private backyard & your very own sparkling in-ground pool! For those who like formality, a Dining room is connected to the Kitchen. The Family Room includes a brick fireplace, built in bookcase/entertainment center & double French doors which lead to not only the Florida Room but also the office area, both of which also overlook the backyard & in-ground pool. The upstairs bedroom area contains 4 bedrooms & a bonus room in which the walls & ceiling are cedar. The master suite is a rather large 650+ SF with the bedroom itself being 20x14 plus a master bath w/whirlpool tub, separate shower/dressing area AND a 240 SF walk-in closet - imagine closing the door to the rest of your life, pouring yourself a glass of wine & taking a relaxing soak in your very own garden tub! Extras include an inside laundry, 2-car attached garage, a 1-car detached garage THREE storage buildings & a green house. Oh, & the neighborhood - it's a family friendly place where you'll meet your neighbors on their daily walking or horse riding excursions through this gorgeous, peaceful tree-filled area full of large & colorfully landscaped properties that are an absolute joy to view any season of the year. You've just gotta see this one!
